Favorites.description: The Lamborghini Veneno Roadster is an ultra-limited-production, open-top supercar known for its aggressive aerodynamic design and exceptional performance.  It's a showcase of Lamborghini's engineering prowess and a symbol of exclusivity.  Only nine were ever produced.
Favorites.engineDetail:
• Configuration: Naturally Aspirated V12
• Displacement: 6.5 liters
• Turbo/Supercharging: None
• Transmission: 7-speed Independent Shifting Rod (ISR)
Favorites.interior:
• Seating: Leather and Alcantara, 2 seats
• Dashboard: Carbon fiber, digital instrument cluster, minimalist design
• Technology:  Advanced electronics, navigation system
• Key Features:  All-wheel drive,  aggressive aerodynamics,  limited production run, naturally aspirated V12 engine.

Favorites.description: The Lamborghini Veneno is an ultra-limited-production, high-performance sports car, built to celebrate Lamborghini's 50th anniversary.  It's known for its aggressive aerodynamic design and exceptional speed and handling.  Only three road-going versions were produced.
Favorites.engineDetail:
• Configuration: 6.5L V12 naturally aspirated
• Displacement: 6.5 liters
• Turbo/Supercharging: None
• Transmission: 7-speed Independent Shifting Rod (ISR)
Favorites.interior:
• Seating: Leather, two seats
• Dashboard:  Digital instrument cluster, minimal controls.
• Technology:  Advanced carbon fiber construction, sophisticated electronics.
• Key Features:  Extreme aerodynamics, all-wheel drive,  limited production exclusivity, carbon fiber monocoque chassis.
